          <text>
            This is going to get worse before it gets better — but at least now we have a chance, because we're working together, even if it's out of necessity rather than trust.

            Florence hasn't moved from her position near the core — she's coordinating, analyzing, adapting to hostile tactics in real time. The plants are following her guidance because they have to — not because they want to, not because they trust her, but because survival matters more than resentment.

            ¶

            For now.
          </text>
